Package edu.mhs.compsys.processors

Contains all IChangeProcessors to pass into recognizer.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DesktopTaskbarChangeProcessor
    This Processor will recognize changes in the desktop and taskbar and quantify those.
    WindowChangeProcessor
    This Processor will recognize changes in the windows and quantify those.
    WindowMenuProcessor
    This Processor will recognize changes in the window-menus and quantify those.
    WindowStateProcessor
    This Processor will recognize changes in windows and quantify those.
